  "title": "The airport personnel spotted a star-like UFO twice at Ponta Grossa Airport [1997]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/23/the-airport-personnel-spotted-a-star-like-ufo-for-the-2nd-time-at-ponta-grossa-airport-1997/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-C0",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 6th, 1997</strong>. Time: 22h20. Duration: 10 to 15 minutes. Three people working at the Ponta Grossa Airport, State of Paraná, observed a star-like UFO at 2,000ft of altitude, flying slowly near one of the airstrips. The unknown object had the appearance of a star changing colors from amber to pink and red, and heading Southwest. It was observed by the naked eye and, according to the report, that was the second time they saw this kind of phenomenon in that region.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.489. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado avistado região do Aeroporto de Ponta Grossa”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
